# 组件与状态

## 组件

- 顺序：`<template>` → `<script setup>` → `<style lang="scss" scoped>`
- Props / Emits 用运行时声明；纯展示组件不发请求

```vue
<template>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h2 class="page-header__title">{{ title }}</h2>
    <button type="button" class="page-header__action" @click="emit('refresh')">
      刷新
    </button>
  </div>
</template>

<script setup>
// 页面标题
const props = defineProps({
  // 标题文案
  title: { type: String, required: true },
})

const emit = defineEmits(['refresh'])
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
.page-header {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 0.75rem;

  &__title {
    margin: 0;
  }
}
</style>
```

## Composables / Pinia

```js
// 用户列表：加载状态与拉取方法
export function useUserList() {
  const list = ref([])
  const loading = ref(false)

  // 按条件请求用户列表
  async function fetchList(params) {}

  return { list, loading, fetchList }
}
```

```js
// 登录态：token、用户信息与退出
export const useAuthStore = defineStore('auth', () => {
  const token = ref(null)
  const user = ref(null)

  // 清空登录态
  function logout() {
    token.value = null
    user.value = null
  }

  return { token, user, logout }
})
```

## SCSS

- 嵌套 + BEM（`&__` / `&--`）；全局变量与断点放 `app/assets/styles/`
- 组件默认可在窄屏正常使用；重型 UI 库按需引入，不默认假定 Element Plus
